Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,Fullmetal Alchemist,0000,0000,0000,,Brotherhood
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,Fullmetal Alchemist,0000,0000,0000,,Episode 33
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,Fullmetal Alchemist,0000,0000,0000,,===============================================================

Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.25,0:01:37.40,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Ed and Al were searching for May, a girl from Xing, to find out more about Eastern Alchemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.10,0:01:41.62,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,They are now headed north after learning she was headed in that direction.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.99,0:01:51.23,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,At the same time, Kimblee, the Crimson Alchemist, is after Scar, who had just left Central and is now westbound.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.38,0:01:58.45,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,But Scar suddenly disappeared in the darkness of the night.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.58,0:02:06.27,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,If they were to jump off the train, it would surely be around here, where the track is full of curves,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.00,0:02:09.54,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,since the engine would decelerate.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.39,0:02:14.82,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,Now the question is, where did they go after they jumped off?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.48,0:02:17.71,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,Have there been any sighting reports on Scar?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.71,0:02:19.53,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,None at all, sir...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.79,0:02:21.36,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,That's very strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.36,0:02:24.53,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,He had been attracting a lot of attention up until this point.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.55,0:02:26.96,Default,Guy2,0000,0000,0000,,Reporting in, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.96,0:02:31.38,Default,Guy2,0000,0000,0000,,A small boat by the river has been stolen about 200 meters south of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.38,0:02:32.54,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Was it Scar?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.54,0:02:34.92,Default,Guy2,0000,0000,0000,,There haven't been any sightings so far.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.92,0:02:35.80,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Go investigate.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.01,0:02:36.78,Default,Guy2,0000,0000,0000,,Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.18,0:02:38.22,Default,Guy3,0000,0000,0000,,Reporting in, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.67,0:02:43.68,Default,Guy3,0000,0000,0000,,We've received a report from an old man, who lives in the area, of two suspicious-looking men heading westbound.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.68,0:02:45.18,Default,Guy4,0000,0000,0000,,Now they're heading west?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.18,0:02:47.56,Default,Guy4,0000,0000,0000,,Send some men over and capture those two immediately!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.76,0:02:48.60,Default,Guy3,0000,0000,0000,,Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.53,0:02:51.84,Default,Guy4,0000,0000,0000,,Is something the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.84,0:02:53.82,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's just that...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.82,0:02:57.94,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,There's a mountain trail on this map that heads north.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.94,0:03:00.14,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,Why is it crossed out?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.60,0:03:03.70,Default,Guy4,0000,0000,0000,,There used to be a path through\Nthe forest to get to the northern area,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.31,0:03:06.74,Default,Guy4,0000,0000,0000,,but it's been closed down due to landslides.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.27,0:03:08.47,Default,Guy4,0000,0000,0000,,What about the path, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.34,0:03:32.15,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,There are several other places beyond this point that have been closed off due to landslides.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.18,0:03:44.61,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like the stream has moved.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.98,0:03:47.78,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,It seems so... but are you saying it means something?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.27,0:03:57.87,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,For an alchemist skilled in destruction, removing an obstacle such as this is a walk in the park.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.68,0:04:05.23,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,It's also simple to destroy the surface of a mountain and to block off the road with the rocks.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.15,0:04:08.89,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Signs of transmutation?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.45,0:04:12.10,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,Send the troops north.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.18,0:04:28.33,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Snow!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.22,0:04:43.46,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.94,0:04:50.46,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Geez, you're so fidgety!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.46,0:04:53.52,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up, I just slipped.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.58,0:04:58.02,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Man, look at all the snow!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.35,0:05:02.28,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. We rarely see snow in Resembool.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.25,0:05:04.58,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah, Al.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.58,0:05:07.66,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Do you remember when it snowed heavily in Resembool when we were kids?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.20,0:05:09.66,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Heavy snowfall?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.61,0:05:14.25,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I remember now!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.57,0:05:16.37,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,We had a snowball fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.43,0:05:19.23,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,We made a snowman, too, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.23,0:05:20.03,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.58,0:05:28.72,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Back then, I never would have thought that I'd come this far north...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.82,0:05:31.85,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,But we did, didn't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.13,0:05:43.90,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Well, what to do now?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.90,0:05:47.36,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,We've still got time until the train to Briggs departs.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.36,0:05:49.98,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you go eat something nice?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.98,0:05:52.35,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not really hungry...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.35,0:05:54.45,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,But I guess I'll go see what's on the menu!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.75,0:05:57.82,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! If you start running, you'll slip again!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.82,0:05:58.37,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.63,0:06:04.37,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Three hours ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.37,0:06:06.63,Default,Guy2,0000,0000,0000,,Scar's description, document number, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.63,0:06:08.22,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,Any new information so far?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.22,0:06:11.76,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,We're trying our best, but we haven't found anything yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.51,0:06:17.61,Default,Guy2,0000,0000,0000,,A man matching Scar's description was sighted at the marshalling yard at the next station.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.61,0:06:19.09,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Is this confirmed?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.09,0:06:20.50,Default,Guy2,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.50,0:06:24.27,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,He was last seen climbing into\Na troop transport headed for Briggs.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.01,0:06:26.57,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,Was there anyone with him?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.57,0:06:28.71,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,A middle-aged man with black hair.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.71,0:06:30.01,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Matches the initial report perfectly.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.27,0:06:32.87,Default,Guy2,0000,0000,0000,,We'll have the train stopped immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.35,0:06:35.40,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,There's no need for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.07,0:06:38.75,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,It would be troublesome if they leap off again.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.81,0:06:48.13,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take over from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.82,0:06:51.89,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't interfere with my work.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.86,0:07:03.44,Default,Scar,0000,0000,0000,,Sleep for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.44,0:07:07.40,Default,Scar,0000,0000,0000,,When we get further north, you'll have\Na hard time sleeping because of the cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.88,0:08:01.86,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,I'm jumping over. Please try to match the speed of the other train.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.86,0:08:02.58,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.44,0:08:28.90,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,Dr. Marcoh.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.41,0:08:31.41,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,I've come to pick you up.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.41,0:08:33.21,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,You've got nowhere else to run.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.21,0:08:35.68,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,Are you alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.68,0:08:37.28,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,Where is Scar?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.65,0:08:40.29,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,You just don't know when to quit, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.86,0:08:44.22,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't I just say you had nowhere else to run, Doctor Mar-
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.02,0:08:49.63,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.40,0:09:02.81,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,So you're the Ishbalan everyone's talking about...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.16,0:09:36.30,Default,Yoki,0000,0000,0000,,You can't expect me to put up with those monsters!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.30,0:09:38.26,Default,Yoki,0000,0000,0000,,Now's my chance to jump off...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.92,0:09:44.02,Default,Yoki,0000,0000,0000,,Impossible...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.71,0:09:59.86,Default,Scar,0000,0000,0000,,Zolf J. Kimblee. The Crimson Alchemist.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.48,0:10:02.62,Default,Scar,0000,0000,0000,,Do you remember me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.62,0:10:05.98,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Very clearly, in fact.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.98,0:10:09.12,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,You were in the Kanda district of Ishbal.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.19,0:10:13.59,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,Was it your family that was around you at the time?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.07,0:10:19.30,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,I believe there was someone who closely resembled you, but with glasses.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.30,0:10:22.88,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,Bleeding heavily from his left abdomen...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.88,0:10:24.72,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,...and writhing in pain...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.85,0:10:38.32,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't good.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.32,0:10:44.74,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,I'm rusty from being in jail for all this time, but he's been fighting since the civil war.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.47,0:10:47.96,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,In terms of stamina, I'm at a disadvantage.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.30,0:10:52.11,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,However, all he can do is destroy-
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.55,0:11:02.72,Default,Scar,0000,0000,0000,,Left abdomen, was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.07,0:11:06.29,Default,Scar,0000,0000,0000,,I won't give you the time to pray.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.46,0:11:10.35,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,It's... a shame...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.77,0:11:15.52,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,That I'd fail to kill the same Ishbalan twice...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.24,0:11:34.33,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,How humiliating that I have to run away...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.84,0:11:38.84,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,We'll settle the match next time, Ishbalan!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.19,0:11:51.24,Default,Scar,0000,0000,0000,,Kimblee!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.90,0:11:55.82,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit, I can't see!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.82,0:11:57.52,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell was that noise?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.55,0:12:08.87,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,One of the cars is missing!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.11,0:12:13.68,Default,Guy2,0000,0000,0000,,We can't! We've been ordered by the army not to stop the train!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.07,0:12:15.66,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,No, we have to!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.66,0:12:18.88,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be our fault if the train derails!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.09,0:12:37.08,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,What... happened to you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.52,0:12:38.11,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.23,0:12:42.76,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,Who the hell said you could stop the train?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.76,0:12:43.45,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.12,0:12:46.28,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,Keep the train running.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.28,0:12:47.74,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,Head north!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.95,0:12:54.75,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,Good... death is chasing me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.75,0:12:59.16,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,Ones who kill are also chased by death.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.00,0:13:03.01,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,Always living alongside death...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.64,0:13:08.12,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,Jobs that risk one's soul are truly beautiful!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.82,0:13:11.51,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,How rewarding...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.25,0:13:14.94,Default,Kim,0000,0000,0000,,My battlefield!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.29,0:13:25.70,Default,May,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if Mr. Scar and Mr. Yoki are all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.70,0:13:32.33,Default,Marcoh,0000,0000,0000,,Since no one has come after us yet, it must mean they're doing a good job drawing the army's attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.33,0:13:33.79,Default,Marcoh,0000,0000,0000,,I hope they're safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.43,0:13:36.66,Default,May,0000,0000,0000,,Dr. Marcoh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.13,0:13:40.45,Default,Marcoh,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's just that...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.45,0:13:42.96,Default,Marcoh,0000,0000,0000,,The northern wind is painful against healing skin.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.96,0:13:48.16,Default,May,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry. I wish I could have healed it to make it look a little better...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.16,0:13:52.64,Default,Marcoh,0000,0000,0000,,No, the face fits me well.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.64,0:13:54.22,Default,Marcoh,0000,0000,0000,,I'm happy with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.53,0:13:57.43,Default,Marcoh,0000,0000,0000,,Take a look, May.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.39,0:13:59.75,Default,May,0000,0000,0000,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.15,0:14:02.03,Default,Marcoh,0000,0000,0000,,They're the Briggs Mountains.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.46,0:14:06.76,Default,Marcoh,0000,0000,0000,,The mountain range that serves as the border between our country and Drakma.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.39,0:14:11.52,Default,Marcoh,0000,0000,0000,,We should be close to the location Scar pointed out...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.52,0:14:12.74,Default,May,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.34,0:14:17.22,Default,May,0000,0000,0000,,We're almost there!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.57,0:14:42.11,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? He checked out of the hotel?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.41,0:14:44.35,Default,Tel,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, just yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.35,0:14:46.27,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know where he went?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.69,0:14:49.48,Default,Tel,0000,0000,0000,,If I recall correctly, he said that they were headed north...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.48,0:14:51.33,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.33,0:14:52.49,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.08,0:14:56.54,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,That idiot...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.98,0:15:00.03,Default,Gar,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong? Were they doing well?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.76,0:15:03.11,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,He said they headed north in that state.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.11,0:15:05.84,Default,Gar,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my! He's totally...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.58,0:15:08.76,Default,Gar,0000,0000,0000,,...gonna die.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.96,0:15:14.57,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Did you catch a cold, Brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.57,0:15:16.07,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,So cold...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.07,0:15:17.97,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,It's Briggs, all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.21,0:15:21.11,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,We're here, boys.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.49,0:15:28.40,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,If you follow this mountain path, you'll get to the Briggs fortress.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.40,0:15:29.28,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.61,0:15:31.36,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah, you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.34,0:15:33.13,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.13,0:15:34.39,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.39,0:15:36.07,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,That's not an automail, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.07,0:15:37.19,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.19,0:15:39.79,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Oh. Then you should be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.10,0:15:43.09,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,What was that about?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.09,0:15:44.22,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,No idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.58,0:15:51.17,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Everything beyond that fence is owned by the army,\Nso you'll die if you stray from the path!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.17,0:15:52.52,Default,Both,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.47,0:15:55.52,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.52,0:15:56.59,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.10,0:16:16.33,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,They say the weather changes rapidly in the mountains, but I never expected something like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.33,0:16:17.89,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,What should we do, Brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.89,0:16:19.87,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,We've completely lost our way.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.19,0:16:21.61,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.61,0:16:27.70,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Master Izumi was thrown into the Briggs Mountains in the winter for a month for her training, and she still survived.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.70,0:16:28.90,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way that could be true!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.90,0:16:31.88,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,How could someone survive for a month out here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.88,0:16:34.39,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,But she said she defeated a bear, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.39,0:16:38.28,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,The bears at Briggs grow to a height of up to two meters!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.28,0:16:40.02,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Who'd be able to defeat one?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.02,0:16:47.94,Default,Both,0000,0000,0000,,A bear!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.88,0:16:58.07,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,That's not a bear!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.30,0:17:01.95,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Al!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.74,0:17:06.22,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hang on!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.22,0:17:08.23,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,You're wearing a military uniform!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.30,0:17:11.45,Default,Bac,0000,0000,0000,,You have an automail, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.45,0:17:13.01,Default,Bac,0000,0000,0000,,Just an ordinary one, it seems.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.09,0:17:16.99,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Yours is just plain ugly!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.99,0:17:20.76,Default,Bac,0000,0000,0000,,How foolish of you to not understand the beauty of this arm!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.39,0:17:26.10,Default,Bac,0000,0000,0000,,Combat Model Automail M1913-A Crocodile.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.85,0:17:32.38,Default,Bac,0000,0000,0000,,Surrender if you don't want to be ripped to shreds, Drakman spy!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.38,0:17:33.64,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Spy?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.64,0:17:35.61,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell are you talking about? I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.15,0:17:36.90,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Why, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.82,0:17:42.08,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Can't you be a little more understanding, oaf?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.68,0:17:45.16,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,What is this pain?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.96,0:17:48.37,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,My automail isn't moving very well!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.50,0:17:50.92,Default,Bac,0000,0000,0000,,You're mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.43,0:17:53.34,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.49,0:17:55.42,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,You bastard...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.58,0:17:57.92,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Just listen to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.92,0:17:59.74,Default,Bac,0000,0000,0000,,You're still going to resist?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.13,0:18:04.10,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Are you serious?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.45,0:18:06.96,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! Wait! Wait! Just listen!!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.96,0:18:09.65,Default,Bac,0000,0000,0000,,Your useless automail is mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.89,0:18:15.17,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,More like, {\i1}your{\i0\fscx30} {\r} arm is mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.81,0:18:19.63,Default,Bac,0000,0000,0000,,Did you do something?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.91,0:18:22.62,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Time out! Time out! Time out! Seriously! Time out!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.14,0:18:25.48,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Why doesn't alchemy work?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.48,0:18:27.00,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't made out of metal?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.26,0:18:28.44,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.88,0:18:32.38,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, Al!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.22,0:18:38.08,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.08,0:18:39.35,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,That freak...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.35,0:18:42.55,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,I would've been killed by Winry before I froze to death out here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.04,0:18:44.65,Default,Bac,0000,0000,0000,,Not bad, brat.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.65,0:18:47.76,Default,Bac,0000,0000,0000,,You did well for having a regular automail.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.76,0:18:49.44,Default,Bac,0000,0000,0000,,But this is it for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.44,0:18:50.06,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.18,0:19:01.34,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Security personnel from Briggs?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.74,0:19:05.72,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Geez, at gunpoint again?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.15,0:19:11.90,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.54,0:19:13.88,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,A wall?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.88,0:19:16.50,Default,Oliv,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter, Captain Buccaneer?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.67,0:19:21.67,Default,Buc,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry for causing such a commotion, Major General Armstrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.41,0:19:30.35,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Armstrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.35,0:19:34.36,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,So that's the person Major Armstrong wanted to introduce to us...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.23,0:19:37.66,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,...Olivier Mira Armstrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.38,0:19:40.72,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Major Armstrong's sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.96,0:19:42.94,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.23,0:19:47.69,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,She looks nothing like him.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.69,0:19:49.25,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,She's not huge.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.81,0:19:51.41,Default,Oliv,0000,0000,0000,,Who the hell are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.18,0:19:55.57,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Edward Elric, the Fullmetal Alchemist.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.06,0:20:01.05,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,I came to see you, Major General, with a letter of introduction from Major Armstrong from Central.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.63,0:20:04.07,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Please get these guys off of us, first!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.12,0:20:06.51,Default,Oliv,0000,0000,0000,,Perform a full body check!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.51,0:20:07.48,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.48,0:20:09.47,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,We're not suspicious in the least bit!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.47,0:20:10.31,Default,Oliv,0000,0000,0000,,How should I know?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.98,0:20:14.69,Default,Oliv,0000,0000,0000,,Anyone can pretend to be someone well-known.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.60,0:20:17.03,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,What?! There's no one in here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.03,0:20:18.17,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,That bitch...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.94,0:20:20.69,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Hm? This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.42,0:20:22.48,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.13,0:20:27.08,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,That's the letter from Major Alex Louis Armstrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.08,0:20:30.88,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,If you read it, you'll know that we're not suspicious at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.56,0:20:34.97,Default,Oliv,0000,0000,0000,,It really is from Alex.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.12,0:20:40.26,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,You're not even going to read it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.26,0:20:43.12,Default,Oliv,0000,0000,0000,,Testimonials mean nothing to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.67,0:20:46.77,Default,Oliv,0000,0000,0000,,I don't need assessments made by others.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.47,0:20:50.14,Default,Oliv,0000,0000,0000,,I'll judge you with my own eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.85,0:21:06.95,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,A-Amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.88,0:21:09.60,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,It's huge...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.60,0:21:11.44,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.46,0:21:14.80,Default,Oliv,0000,0000,0000,,Come in, Fullmetal Alchemist.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.80,0:21:18.00,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Awesome! It's so tall! It's huge!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.54,0:21:21.40,Default,Oliv,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up and walk, laggards.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.40,0:21:23.97,Default,Oliv,0000,0000,0000,,Want me to rip that antenna off your head?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.00,0:21:31.60,Default,Oliv,0000,0000,0000,,I'll tell you this now. I won't be treating you like a kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.25,0:21:35.14,Default,Oliv,0000,0000,0000,,This is Briggs, the land of natural defense.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.05,0:21:38.20,Default,Oliv,0000,0000,0000,,A world where the weak are victims of the strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.23,0:23:20.02,Default,May,0000,0000,0000,,There it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.57,0:23:32.07,Default,Marcoh,0000,0000,0000,,So these are his brother's research documents.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.07,0:23:37.33,Default,May,0000,0000,0000,,A combination of the alchemies from Xing and Amestris.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.33,0:23:40.02,Default,May,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if there's anything about immortality in here?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.02,0:23:42.00,Default,Marcoh,0000,0000,0000,,I hope there is.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.76,0:23:49.86,Default,Marcoh,0000,0000,0000,,Now, will this become a book of hope,\Nor will it turn out to be a book of despair...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.84,0:23:55.96,Default,Marcoh,0000,0000,0000,,Let's begin the analysis.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.94,0:24:02.96,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,The general of Briggs, Olivier Mira Armstrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.96,0:24:07.91,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Fierce and powerful, she is Amestris' guardian of the north.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.50,0:24:12.32,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,She has no fears, though there are many that fear her.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.42,0:24:17.64,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Next time, Fullmetal Alchemist:
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.64,0:24:21.64,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Episode 34, Ice Queen.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.48,0:24:24.85,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,This is how we do things in Briggs.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.85,0:24:27.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
